name: TFSI Engine
description: This was a wonderful model. Took longer than advertised, but that was what I wanted. Many more fastener are provided than you need. Everything is in the box. Costs a lot, but the value is there.

name: Bilstein EVO
description: seem to be good quality and good bushings with the kit, spent a couple hours trying to remove the camber bolts in the upper control arms finally the Sawzall fixed them and it was worth the 2000$ for new camber bolts everything went back together fast and easy.

name: Getrag 6EM
description: I have never rebuilt a transmission prior to reading this book and using for direction. I was able to to do my transmission rebuild with only the cost of the parts. Trans works better than it ever has.

name: Brake XLKr
description: The rotors and pads in this set for both front and rear fit perfectly. I am really pleased with the braking performance of these pads and rotors and the price is spectacular.
